# OpenAPI Contract-First Rule

This project is contract-first.

Before creating or changing controller request/response DTOs:

1. Update `src/main/resources/openapi/log-stream-service.yaml`

2. Regenerate OpenAPI sources with Maven

3. Implement the generated API interface

4. Do not hand-write controller DTOs when generated models already exist

Controllers should implement generated interfaces from:

`com.logstream.generated.api`

Generated models should come from:

`com.logstream.generated.model`

Business logic belongs in service implementations paired with service interfaces, not controllers.